1.    Be quiet – Don’t disturb others.
    2.    No loud talking or yelling – Keep your voice low.
    3.    No background noise – No music, static, or annoying sounds.
    4.    Respect others’ sleep – Let people rest.
    5.    No spam or trolling – Don’t make unnecessary noises or messages.
    6.    Quiet chatting is okay – Whispering or soft talking is allowed if it doesn’t disturb others.
    7.    Mods have the final say – Follow their instructions.
